yle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2650000/2651435/carn20180228001_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2650000%2F2651435%2Fcarn20180228001_1024.jpg&h=3d7c3d09&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"地中海：唔洗周圍望啦，一齊執定野返大灣區啦，外國無你份架啦"},{"pid":"a8cd80cc5582f7a227f6c84205f0a3e99a781a4c","tid":2032650,"uid":8014,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:29:40.000Z","msg":"諗住呃邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n評級機構穆迪分析指香港沒有展現具體計劃處理香港市民所反映的政治、經濟以及社會問題，本港管治能力不及該行原先評估，也可能是本港自治權較原先估計有更大限制。"},{"pid":"aa3dde8612d2376cd21b7bc7bd036205da118538","tid":2032650,"uid":235277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:29:49.000Z","msg":"傻既先信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d921fb9f9c236e7abeba37b60f1c5146d9b019","tid":2032650,"uid":82125,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"上年個逃犯條例都搞唔掂，今年仲解釋d乜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb8a639ee92b519ba1764bca6884e444e9b2c35","tid":2032650,"uid":44358,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">以抗衡<strong>反華勢力</strong>和反政府人士正動員的無理攻擊和肆意詆毀。</span><br />\n<br />\n１） 預定自己一定係制裁之列，所以唔怕學中蟈，講反華勢力。<br />\n<br />\n２）佢句說話，預定美國一定會制裁香港，依家只係想安撫人心。<br />\n<br />\n３）有錢既手足，一定要轉錢走，覆巢之下無完卵。"},{"pid":"efa8100d2e2bf0642a9d0139226875f506ae7ed7","tid":2032650,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:30:10.000Z","msg":"轉場五毛，冇人五毛，可以收皮喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2032603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2032603</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7cf608e7cf3b0532e3fea8572c55c45088ea9941","tid":2032650,"uid":124180,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTi