委會制定建立健全香港特區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制，在香港公布實施，是有必要性及迫切性。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，近月有不少市民提出特區應盡快啟動《基本法》23條的立法工作，但是質疑立法會近乎被癱瘓，還有沒有能力通過任何維護國家安全的法律。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，會和團隊盡全力向公眾宣傳和解釋這次為國家安全立法的重要性，以抗衡反華勢力和反政府人士正動員的無理攻擊和肆意詆毀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528032-20200524.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528032-20200524.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a6176dd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528032-20200524.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c35f146c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528032-20200524.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c2AigJZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2AigJZ.jpg&h=fe196cf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:34:05.000Z","msg":"特首係女架咩？駱生呢？"},{"pid":"8dace37cddfde0bb7a7c0752b05512262096ed92","tid":2032650,"uid":186431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:34:58.000Z","msg":"你當人哋弱智定你自己弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f45e5dab69763dc555694add6d0963df314998a","tid":2032650,"uid":264426,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"叫佢搞獨立調查委員會即係反華；<br />\n叫佢落台就分裂國家；<br />\n咁叫包子落台咪分裂共產黨?"},{"pid":"fddab29d33227184a2b7408345a21afb94dd5266","tid":2032650,"uid":14449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"全部留言都係支持林鄭<br />\n條友仲圍爐過連登仔"},{"pid":"4feaacdd24951c5ba751cf2e4bed8dcbdd1b0d88","tid":2032650,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"894435fa9d15a41dfb49f7ef369bbf4681c978ff","tid":2032650,"uid":155095,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:27:34.000Z","msg":"唔知林鄭手下係唔係咁諗呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2650000/2651435/carn20180228001_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2650000%2F2651435%2Fcarn20180228001_1024.jpg&h=3d7c3d09&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"佢班仆街準備享受大灣區榮耀啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=cff7a184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"7c28e9cfadf3985f42a1831261a4