0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"誰不擁護國安法<br />\n誰就反共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0c77b80215946320ec3b9e059ff6e22a5a43a1","tid":2032650,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:02:12.000Z","msg":"弱智會信"},{"pid":"31f8e9ca7f60632f8cf8ccb495e56150e2becf28","tid":2032650,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:02:58.000Z","msg":"盡你老母力咩，逃犯條例攪撚到一鑊粥，我係共產黨第一個郁你個八婆"},{"pid":"c5d65c8df2ce6f23569a99e68c2807f06ee1ab47","tid":2032650,"uid":22535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83eaa02c817b2b3d711bff223ea6a4536d32c5bd","tid":2032650,"uid":276175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5eca6c1fcc59f9c2a6607312c1e6c3d4a5e5674f","tid":2032650,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:24:23.000Z","msg":"特首：盡力解釋國安法重要性 抗衡反政府人士肆意詆毀<br />\n2020-05-24 HKT 15:18<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在社交專頁發文，指全國人大主動出手，授權全國人大常委會制定建立健全香港特區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制，在香港公布實施，是有必要性及迫切性。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，近月有不少市民提出特區應盡快啟動《基本法》23條的立法工作，但是質疑立法會近乎被癱瘓，還有沒有能力通過任何維護國家安全的法律。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，會和團隊盡全力向公眾宣傳和解釋這次為國家安全立法的重要性，以抗衡反華勢力和反政府人士正動員的無理攻擊和肆意詆毀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528032-20200524.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528032-20200524.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a6176dd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528032-20200524.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c35f146c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528032-20200524.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c2AigJZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2AigJZ.jpg&h=fe196cf2&s={SI